disclaimer.subtitle: Reviews from past guests help our community learn more about each home. By default, reviews are sorted by relevancy. Relevancy is based on recency, length, and information that you provide to us, such as your booking search, your country, and your language preferences. Only the guest who booked the reservation can leave a review, and Airbnb only moderates reviews flagged for not following our policies. To be eligible for a percentile ranking or guest favorite label, listings need at least 5 reviews in the last 4 years. Criteria is subject to change. Learn more in our Help Center

htmlDescription.htmlText:
Meticulously maintained "Mansion" sleeps up to 30 with 11 BR and 6.5 BA on 8 acres. There is both a main house and a guest house. The main house consists of 7 BR and 4.5 BA with over 5000 square feet of living space. The guest house has an additional 2000 square ft, which includes 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. Gameroom has pool table, poker table, shuffleboard, and home theater room! Free WIFI throughout. Basketball/Pickleball Court, Putting Green, Fire Pit on 8 Private Acres. Free Tesla EV Charger!

The space
Bedroom Details:

Bedroom #1 King Bed Main House Main Floor
Bedroom #2 Queen Bed Main House Main Floor
Bedroom #3 Queen Bed Main House Main Floor
Bedroom #4 Queen Bed Main House 2nd Floor
Bedroom #5 (2) Queen Beds Main House 2nd Floor
Bedroom #6 (2) Queen Beds Main House 2nd Floor
Bedroom #7 (1) Queen Bed (1) Twin Bed Main House Lower Level
Bedroom #8 (1) Queen Bed Guest House 2nd FL
Bedroom #9 (1) Queen Bed Guest House 2nd FL
Bedroom #10 (1) Queen Bed (1) Twin Bed Guest House 2nd FL
Bedroom #11 (1) Queen Bed (1) Twin Bed Guest House 2nd FL

Bathroom Details:

Bathroom #1 Toilet, Tub, Shower Main House Master Suite
Bathroom #2 Toilet, Shower Main House En Suite
Bathroom #3 Toilet, Tub, Shower Main House 2nd Level
Bathroom #4 Toilet, Shower Main House Lower Level
Bathroom #5 Toilet Main House Main Level
Bathroom #6 Toilet, Tub, Shower Guest House 1st Floor
Bathroom #7 Toilet, Shower Guest House 2nd Floor

Guest access
Guests have access to the entire home. This includes the hot tub, pool table, grill, all bedrooms, bathrooms, washer & dryer, indoor fireplace and outdoor fire pit, front and back decks. The home is "turn key." Linens, pillows and kitchen appliances are provided. The guest will only need their shower and bath needs. If you have a question about what is provided at the home, just ask!

Other things to note
We provide bed linens
2 rolls of paper towels and 1 roll of toilet paper per bathroom.
We DO NOT provide bath towels or hand towels.

No prom rentals or senior week rentals.
Must be 25 years of age or older to book.
